               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380514-name-1328" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1328" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1328" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1328" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I was on a visit at Mr. Mason's, at Deptford. On the 25th of April an alarm was given by my wife's sister that the window was open—I ran out, and on going down Grove-street I saw two young met—I made towards them—to the best of my belief the prisoner was one of them—they divided—one came towards me without a bundle—the pri<lb></lb>soner went on with the bundle—I walked after him—he walked fast, I began to run—he dropped the bundle and ran on—a man took him—I picked up the bundle, and it contained these two cloaks and the shawl—two of them are my wife's—I will not be positive the prisoner is the lad who dropped the bundle, but I believe he is.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380514-name-1329" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1329" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1329" type="surname" value="GRIFFITHS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1329" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE GRIFFITHS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Deptford. I saw the prosecutor running after the prisoner, crying "Stop thief,"—he dropped this bundle close by me—I am certain he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18380514-name-1330" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1330" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1330" type="surname" value="WALL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380514-name-1330" type="given" value="FRANCIS"></interp>FRANCIS WALL</persName>
                  </hi>. I saw the prisoner running towards the Plough-bridge—he ran and concealed himself under the palings.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. He did not see me running. I did not have the bundle at all—the witness said he could not swear to me at all.</p>
